summary: This is a U.S. Customs and Border Protection TECS travel record listing passengers and crew on a private flight from Paris (LFPB) to Teterboro, NJ (KTEB) on September 6, 2018. The document shows Jeffrey Epstein and David Rodgers as travelers on the flight.

events.description: Jeffrey Epstein and David Rodgers traveled via private air from Paris Le Bourget Airport (LFPB) to Teterboro Airport, New Jersey (KTEB).

keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein traveled on a private flight from Paris to Teterboro, NJ on September 6, 2018.
David Neville Rodgers was listed as crew on the same flight.
The travel record was generated by U.S. Customs and Border Protection's TECS system on April 23, 2019.
The flight originated from Paris Le Bourget Airport (LFPB) and arrived at Teterboro Airport (KTEB).
